                    <span>This is nice reading but if you are interested in learning some strategies for you poker game against you buddies on Friday night, this isn't for you.  If you are going to be playing in tourneys against strong players, then read it.  He has some unique strategies which will steal you some pots.  </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">maybe the best how to</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
